{"tid":842622,"cid":15,"subCid":0,"title":"二手成交：減價續現！新屯門中心累劈95萬沽 (低估價20%)","createTime":"2018-09-30T12:59:04.000Z","updateTime":"2018-10-01T16:37:06.000Z","uid":83582,"like":9,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":22,"replies":[{"pid":"b6cb8b6e1273ce7b1c7bbd7df0ac9b1d6cf18f12","tid":842622,"uid":83582,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-30T12:59:04.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/scare.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n09月30日(日) 14:12<br />\n<br />\n二手成交：減價續現！新屯門中心累劈95萬沽<br />\n<br />\n二手市業主繼續減價，祥益黃慶德表示，屯門新屯門中心3座高層C室，實用464方呎，原業主放盤兩個月，原叫價580萬元，因應市道變化，加上區內一手價錢低開，銀行加息，業主態度軟化，業主累積減價95萬元，終以485萬元售出，呎價10,453元。據了解，<span style=\"color: red;\">有個別銀行對上址估價逾600萬元</span>。"},{"pid":"89e15d72a20c4ea58f2f5dd00f5073bfdbac76e6","tid":842622,"uid":83582,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-30T13:00:47.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"http://hk.on.cc/hk/bkn/cnt/finance/20180930/bkn-20180930141253295-0930_00842_001.html\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fhk.on.cc%2Fhk%2Fbkn%2Fcnt%2Ffinance%2F20180930%2Fbkn-20180930141253295-0930_00842_001.html&d=HsndlIiz%2Fi%2Fc61jSc1ST0ozZXVCnaYNE8CBFJ%2F%2FgXXY%3D&h=e61cc281\" target=\"_blank\">http://hk.on.cc/hk/bkn/cnt/finance/20180930/bkn-20180930141253295-0930_00842_001.html</a>"},{"pid":"c7add5f97abba9684eab244e31ea29aff4cc1c63","tid":842622,"uid":104714,"like":13,"dislike":0,"score":13,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-30T13:02:05.000Z","msg":"屯門唔計"},{"pid":"cd693789c3b46eb3e619ff909b34bd46347a4421","tid":842622,"uid":28245,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-30T13:02:09.000Z","msg":"要走好走 好快跌兩城"},{"pid":"e7c71ee60f10522a0680a293aabcdeb36c2a9634","tid":842622,"uid":115468,"like":21,"dislike":0,"score":21,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-09-30T13:03:23.000Z","msg":"大西北唔計<br />\n高層唔計<br />\n低過銀行估價唔計<br />\n星期日唔計<br />\n聽日國慶唔計"},{"pid":"f536e43571064804a9752a4bcf0b449a88adb6c1","tid":842622,"uid":132587,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyT